25
00:00:56.970 --> 00:00:59.950
and then simply walk through that installer.

26
00:00:59.950 --> 00:01:03.600
It's a standard installer, nothing special there.

27
00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:06.600
Now, once you did install Visual Studio Code

28
00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:07.940
you can open it.

29
00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:09.280
And once you did open it,

30
00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:11.940
it will look something like this.

31
00:01:11.940 --> 00:01:13.870
Now the exact look can differ

32
00:01:13.870 --> 00:01:16.350
but it should look something like this.

