00:01:35.830 --> 00:01:39.410
And you can simply open the React projects

40
00:01:39.410 --> 00:01:42.160
you are going to work on throughout this course

41
00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:43.880
with this editor.

42
00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:46.480
So at this point we don't have a project yet.

43
00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:48.350
Later once we do have projects,

44
00:01:48.350 --> 00:01:50.930
simply open those project folders

45
00:01:50.930 --> 00:01:52.510
with this editor,

46
00:01:52.510 --> 00:01:55.173
and you'll then be able to work on your code.

47
00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:58.740
Now regarding the settings and the styling

48
00:01:58.740 --> 00:02:00.480
and the look of this editor

